name: Yoshida Density App
description:
The Hands-on Portal Digital Dashboard Space Density Application Webble

Old Hands-on Portal application using the old version of the DigitalDashboard.

This Webble app loads a few DigitalDashboard components, connects them, and loads some data. Sets up a visualization environment that can show 3D space density data.
